    <stitle>EC-16 CONTROLLER - TROUBLESHOOTING - TESTING FOR FALSE INDICATION CAUSED BY WHEEL SPEED COMPONENTS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="hl0403217" svcproctype="troubleshoot" graphiccount="0">
        <title>TESTING FOR FALSE INDICATION CAUSED BY WHEEL SPEED COMPONENTS</title>
        <table id="hl0403237">
            <title>Testing For False Indication Caused By Wheel Speed Components</title>
            <tgroup cols="5">
                <colspec colname="1" colwidth="0.77in"/>
                <colspec colname="2" colwidth="0.84in"/>
                <colspec colname="3" colwidth="2.19in"/>
                <colspec colname="4" colwidth="1.27in"/>
                <colspec colname="5" colwidth="1.30in"/>
                <spanspec namest="1" nameend="5" spanname="s1t5"/>
                <thead>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">STEP</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">KEY</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">ACTION</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">YES-IN SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">NO-OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>With ignition ON, hold magnet on EC-16 RESET and note LEDs. Are all LEDs
                                illuminated?
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Replace the EC-16.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On/Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Remove magnet. Turn the ignition OFF and inspect appropriate axle and wheel for
                                presence of an exciter or tone ring and speed sensor. Check sensor "gap" (distance
                                between speed sensor and exciter ring) and bearing end play. Re-adjust as necessary. Run
                                vehicle at 7 MPH or more for 5 seconds or more. Turn ignition OFF. Repeat
                                <hotlnk document="s04032_HL0403208.xml" xrefid="hl0403208">INITIAL START-UP
                                    PROCEDURE</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
